-- Berkshire’s MidAmerican Creates Renewables Unit, Led by Fehrman
-- B y   N o a h   B u h a y a r
-- 2012-01-24T13:18:44Z
-- http://www.bloomberg.com/news/2012-01-24/berkshire-s-midamerican-creates-renewables-unit-led-by-fehrman.html
Berkshire Hathaway Inc. (BRK/A) ’s energy
unit established a new business to aid investments in
unregulated renewable generation, including wind, geothermal,
solar and hydroelectric projects.  Bill Fehrman was named president of the new renewables
unit, according to a Business Wire statement today from Omaha,
Nebraska-based Berkshire’s MidAmerican Energy Holdings Co.  To contact the reporter on this story:
Noah Buhayar in New York at 
